author: Paul Cullen
title: Coronavirus: Most deaths have been in settings such as hospitals and nursing homes
description: Experts due to meet again on Friday to discuss possible further measures to curb spread of virus
content:
Ten more patients with Covid-19 have died, by far the highest daily death toll so far in the outbreak.
